title: RealArcade - Hollywood Tycoon - Wendy99
description:
Be a movie mogul in Hollywood Tycoon, the game that lets you build and run your very own dream 
factory! Select the best script, pick out the perfect actor, and hope for a blockbuster in this 
original challenge that puts you in charge of every production. Develop and produce epic 
romances, terrifying thrillers, hilarious comedies and more. Or, mix them all up and create the 
craziest cinema in town. Featuring a fun musical score, fantastic graphics, and endless 
possibilities, Hollywood Tycoon is your ticket to fun.
